OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FOfsted inspections require 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fmore empathy - new boss    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The body overseeing school inspections 
OL,6, must listen to the criticism it has    
OL,7, received following the suicide of head 
OL,8, teacher Ruth Perry, its new chief says.
OL,10,FA coroner ruled a critical Ofsted      
OL,11,Freport contributed to her death.       
OL,13,FSir Martyn Oliver said Ofsted had to   
OL,14,Fensure high standards but admitted it  
OL,15,Fcould also be "far more empathetic".   
OL,17,FInspectors will receive training around
OL,18,Fmental health at the start of this new 
OL,19,Fterm, meaning no routine inspections   
OL,20,Fwill happen until later in January.    
